PREREQUISITES

In order to install and use this package you will need:

XML::Parser >=2.31
Symmetrix box with VCM enabled *)
WideSky 5.1 or higher with "Device masking" option licensed via symlmf
/opt/emc/WideSky/*/bin in your $PATH



INSTALLATION

Just follow the usual procedure:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


-------------------------------
*) Be sure that you can see VCM device - verify with vcmfind command.
   If vcmfind failed, try execute "symcfg discover" and try execute "vcmfind" again.
